WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.500
One abstraction sits behind sixty-eight payment gateways, and this dashboard tracks every one of them live.

2
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:14.100
Every provider carries its real status — sandbox-ready, mock mode, or KYC-gated — nothing here is faked.

3
00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:20.100
Tap a gateway and the run begins — the payment is journaled to Room before the SDK even opens.

4
00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:26.800
The client reports success, but that's only a hint — the timeline won't settle until the server verifies it.

5
00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:31.600
The everyday checkout runs through that same orchestrator, just wrapped in a cart.

6
00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:40.200
Every transaction lands in that same Room journal, filterable by status — success, failed, refunded, all streamed live.

7
00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:48.000
Real logos where they're licensed, a generated monogram everywhere else — sixty-eight gateways, zero broken badges.

8
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:54.900
And it isn't Android-only — the same contract, the same guarantees, running natively on iOS as well.
